<h2>Chas Skelly</h2>
<p>Skelly was a famous high school/ college wrestling fighter. His record is as impressive as  164 victorys with only 3 losses. With this strong wrestling foundation Skelly tends to make use of strong strikes like his over hand and left hook, for example.</p>

<p>The texas-born fighter will step in the octagon this saturday with 5 victories in his 7 fights under the UFC banner. Of his total 15 wins, 8 have come by the way of submission. Chas Skelly don’t really mind getting punched and will be pleasure to start a good fist brawl</p>

<h5>Last fight</h5>
<h4>Darren Elkins x Chas Skelly 05.03.2016</h4>
